      <title>初识知识图谱</title>
      <link href="/2023/07/14/page/"/>
      <url>/2023/07/14/page/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>知识图谱可用于搜索引擎的开发、人工智能领域。</p><h1 id="所需工具"><a href="#所需工具" class="headerlink" title="所需工具"></a>所需工具</h1><ol><li><p>语言：用python的话会比较方便操作</p></li><li><p>数据库：数据库大多使用neo4j，一种图形数据库，有可视化界面，可以看语句执行后的效果（目前使用社区版）</p></li><li><p>neo4j相关教程可以参考neo4j手册(<a href="https://www.w3cschool.cn/neo4j/">neo4j 教程_w3cschool</a>)</p></li></ol><h2 id="增删改查（基本操作）"><a href="#增删改查（基本操作）" class="headerlink" title="增删改查（基本操作）"></a>增删改查（基本操作）</h2><p>入门neo4j数据库的话，初步要掌握增删改查</p><ul><li><p>增</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">create (n:标签名 &#123;属性:，属性:&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">例子：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">create (n:person&#123;name:&quot;zangsan&quot;,age:20&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>删（删除某一实体）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">create (n:标签名 &#123;属性:，属性:&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">match (n:标签名 &#123;属性:，属性:&#125;) delete n</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>例子：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">create (n:person&#123;name:&quot;zangsan&quot;,age:20&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">match (n:person&#123;name:&quot;zangsan&quot;&#125;) delete n</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>删（关系）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">match(m:person（标签名）&#123;name（属性）:&quot;lisi&quot;,age（属性）:&quot;19&quot;&#125;)-[a:关系名]-&gt;(n:person&#123;name:&quot;zhangsan&quot;,age:&quot;20&quot;&#125;) delete a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意：想要删除某个实体要先删除其与另外实体之间的关系，上面的n、m、a等均为代指，无具体规则，-&gt;即为实际操作语句中的→箭头。</p></li><li><p>改（加标签）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">match (k:person) where id(i)=值 set k:新增标签名 return k</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>改（加属性）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">match (k:person) where id(i)=值 set k.属性名=值 return k</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>改（修改属性）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">match (k:person) where id(i)=值 set k.属性名=改后值 return k</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>查（实际用的最多，较复杂建议多参考手册和neo4j提供的例子）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">match (n:person)-[:关系名]-&gt;(m:person) return n,m</span><br><span class="line">上述查的操作还是比较简单的</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>快速清除数据库（删除所有实体和关系）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">MATCH(n)</span><br><span class="line">DETACH DELETE n </span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h1 id="一个简单例子"><a href="#一个简单例子" class="headerlink" title="一个简单例子"></a>一个简单例子</h1><p>我们列举几个关于三国的人物，添加了归属地属性，并建立了人物间的关系。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">创建实体并添加属性</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">CREATE (:Character &#123;name: &#x27;刘备&#x27;, kingdom: &#x27;蜀&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (:Character &#123;name: &#x27;关羽&#x27;, kingdom: &#x27;蜀&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (:Character &#123;name: &#x27;张飞&#x27;, kingdom: &#x27;蜀&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (:Character &#123;name: &#x27;诸葛亮&#x27;, kingdom: &#x27;蜀&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (:Character &#123;name: &#x27;赵云&#x27;, kingdom: &#x27;蜀&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (:Character &#123;name: &#x27;曹操&#x27;, kingdom: &#x27;魏&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (:Character &#123;name: &#x27;张辽&#x27;, kingdom: &#x27;魏&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (:Character &#123;name: &#x27;许褚&#x27;, kingdom: &#x27;魏&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (:Character &#123;name: &#x27;郭嘉&#x27;, kingdom: &#x27;魏&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (:Character &#123;name: &#x27;孙权&#x27;, kingdom: &#x27;吴&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (:Character &#123;name: &#x27;周瑜&#x27;, kingdom: &#x27;吴&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (:Character &#123;name: &#x27;陆逊&#x27;, kingdom: &#x27;吴&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">创建关系</span><br><span class="line">由于其中a和b参数相同，每一个关系创建就要运行一次</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">MATCH (a:Character &#123;name: &#x27;刘备&#x27;&#125;), (b:Character &#123;name: &#x27;关羽&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (a)-[:BROTHER]-&gt;(b)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (b)-[:BROTHER]-&gt;(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">MATCH (a:Character &#123;name: &#x27;刘备&#x27;&#125;), (b:Character &#123;name: &#x27;张飞&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (a)-[:BROTHER]-&gt;(b)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (b)-[:BROTHER]-&gt;(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">MATCH (a:Character &#123;name: &#x27;刘备&#x27;&#125;), (b:Character &#123;name: &#x27;诸葛亮&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (a)-[:COUNSELOR]-&gt;(b)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (b)-[:LORD]-&gt;(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">MATCH (a:Character &#123;name: &#x27;刘备&#x27;&#125;), (b:Character &#123;name: &#x27;赵云&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (a)-[:FOLLOWER]-&gt;(b)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (b)-[:LORD]-&gt;(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">MATCH (a:Character &#123;name: &#x27;曹操&#x27;&#125;), (b:Character &#123;name: &#x27;张辽&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (a)-[:GENERAL]-&gt;(b)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (b)-[:LORD]-&gt;(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">MATCH (a:Character &#123;name: &#x27;曹操&#x27;&#125;), (b:Character &#123;name: &#x27;许褚&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (a)-[:GENERAL]-&gt;(b)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (b)-[:LORD]-&gt;(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">MATCH (a:Character &#123;name: &#x27;曹操&#x27;&#125;), (b:Character &#123;name: &#x27;郭嘉&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (a)-[:COUNSELOR]-&gt;(b)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (b)-[:LORD]-&gt;(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">MATCH (a:Character &#123;name: &#x27;孙权&#x27;&#125;), (b:Character &#123;name: &#x27;周瑜&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (a)-[:COUNSELOR]-&gt;(b)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (b)-[:LORD]-&gt;(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">MATCH (a:Character &#123;name: &#x27;孙权&#x27;&#125;), (b:Character &#123;name: &#x27;陆逊&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (a)-[:COUNSELOR]-&gt;(b)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (b)-[:LORD]-&gt;(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">MATCH (a:Character &#123;name: &#x27;曹操&#x27;&#125;), (b:Character &#123;name: &#x27;孙权&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (a)-[:ENEMY]-&gt;(b)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (b)-[:ENEMY]-&gt;(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">MATCH (a:Character &#123;name: &#x27;曹操&#x27;&#125;), (b:Character &#123;name: &#x27;刘备&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (a)-[:ENEMY]-&gt;(b)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (b)-[:ENEMY]-&gt;(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">MATCH (a:Character &#123;name: &#x27;孙权&#x27;&#125;), (b:Character &#123;name: &#x27;刘备&#x27;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (a)-[:ALLY]-&gt;(b)</span><br><span class="line">CREATE (b)-[:ALLY]-&gt;(a)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果图如下：</p><p><img src="D:\HexoBlog\source\pic\三国.png" alt="三国"></p><p>在这个知识图谱中，曹操、孙权和刘备被创建为三个节点，并且彼此之间建立了关系。曹操和孙权之间是敌对关系，所以他们之间的边标记为”ENEMY”。曹操和刘备之间也是敌对关系，同样标记为”ENEMY”。而孙权和刘备之间是盟友关系，标记为”ALLY”。</p><p>你可以根据需要继续添加其他人物角色以及他们之间的关系。</p><p>请注意，这只是一个简单的示例，实际的知识图谱可以更加丰富和复杂。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
